{
  "id": "69a9e5d0a3e2d916688c5b85",
  "title": "強い言葉を書いてけ",
  "created": 1772742102,
  "updated": 1772804293,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a9e5d0a3e2d916688c5b85",
      "text": "強い言葉を書いてけ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742102,
      "updated": 1772742114
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e5e50000000000b61728",
      "text": "[強い言葉]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742118,
      "updated": 1772742122
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e5e10000000000b61726",
      "text": "#書いてけ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742114,
      "updated": 1772742118
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9f33e0000000000b61753",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772745534,
      "updated": 1772745534
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9f33e0000000000b61754",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772745534,
      "updated": 1772745541
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e5e20000000000b61727",
      "text": "\t[ようこそ愚かなホモサピエンス]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742115,
      "updated": 1772745559
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9f3920000000000b61756",
      "text": "\t最初からDropboxに入れとけばよかったのに、[未来の見えない愚かなホモサピエンス]ですね",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772745619,
      "updated": 1772745653
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9f3930000000000b61757",
      "text": " [なんとでも取れるような曖昧な言説を弄して何か考えてるような気持ちになる]なんて愚かなホモサピエンスですね",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772745619,
      "updated": 1772745642
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9f3460000000000b61755",
      "text": "　バクテリアに「自分たちがいかにホモサピエンスから劣っているか」を理解する能力がないように、ホモサピエンスにも「自分たちがいかに我々から劣っているか」を理解する能力はないのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772745543,
      "updated": 1772768968
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa4ec5000000000003786f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772768966,
      "updated": 1772768966
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa6600000000004ca50e",
      "text": "🇯🇵",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792424,
      "updated": 1772792428
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa6c00000000004ca50f",
      "text": "\t[遺憾砲]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792429,
      "updated": 1772792434
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7200000000004ca510",
      "text": "\t 1. [懸念]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792435,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca511",
      "text": "  2. [強く懸念]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca512",
      "text": "  3. [憂慮]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca513",
      "text": "  4. [深く憂慮]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca514",
      "text": "  5. [遺憾]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca515",
      "text": "  6. [極めて遺憾]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca516",
      "text": "  7. [非難]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa7300000000004ca517",
      "text": "  8. [断固避難]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792436,
      "updated": 1772792436
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa6600000000004ca50d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772792423,
      "updated": 1772792423
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e5eb0000000000b61729",
      "text": "[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742123,
      "updated": 1772742124
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef0c0000000000b61751",
      "text": "いたたまれなくなったのでモザイクを掛けておく",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772744460,
      "updated": 1772744475
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef5c0000000000b61752",
      "text": "\t[~ [一挙一動に言いがかりをつけ]て妨害することを繰り返す「[腐った果実]」がいるコミュニティはしまいには誰も自由に発言できなくなり[優秀な人から先に消えていく]という経験則がある]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772744541,
      "updated": 1772744688
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e6d30000000000b61733",
      "text": "\t[~ [このような行為は単に無能であるばかりか有害でさえある]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742356,
      "updated": 1772742599
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e72e0000000000b61734",
      "text": "\t[~ 特性を詳しく把握することなく[「参考までに」当てにしている]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742447,
      "updated": 1772742454
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e5eb0000000000b6172a",
      "text": "\t[~ [人間の自己申告は八割がたでたらめにすぎない]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742123,
      "updated": 1772742330
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e6350000000000b6172d",
      "text": "\t[~ [誰も視界に映る物事全てを詳しく検討し直すことはない]が、一方で[“誰かしら”のいうことを自身の文脈に読み替えてそのまま持論にしてしまう]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742198,
      "updated": 1772742335
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e6540000000000b6172e",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 誰かが[自身の都合で誤読]するだろうことは避けようがない]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742229,
      "updated": 1772742339
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e6650000000000b6172f",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 人間はどこにも[書かれていないことを読み取]ってしまう生き物である]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742245,
      "updated": 1772742342
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e6730000000000b61730",
      "text": "\t[~ [お前と一緒にしないでほしい]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742260,
      "updated": 1772742346
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e67e0000000000b61731",
      "text": "\t[~ [自己啓発bot]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742271,
      "updated": 1772742350
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e5f20000000000b6172c",
      "text": "\t[~ [暗黙の前提を自明視する人間には自我がない]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742130,
      "updated": 1772742353
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa653a0000000000decdef",
      "text": "\t[~ （お前に対する）[すべては無意味]だった]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772774715,
      "updated": 1772791680
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6d7a0000000000154de1",
      "text": "\t> 【…】[人権の無視及び軽侮が、人類の良心を踏みにじった野蛮行為をもたらし、言論及び信仰の自由が受けられ、恐怖及び欠乏のない世界の到来が、一般の人々の最高の願望として宣言された]【…】——[世界人権宣言　前文]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772776826,
      "updated": 1772791693
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac32b00000000004ca77d",
      "text": "\t[Summer498.icon][{ [もっと勉強してからお話になったらいかがですか]][!. [Nrem.icon]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772798764,
      "updated": 1772798830
    },
    {
      "id": "69aad6d10000000000a9d4f0",
      "text": "\t[これ読んでると人はなぜ生きるんだろうという気がしてくる]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772803794,
      "updated": 1772803795
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9e6cf0000000000b61732",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772742352,
      "updated": 1772742352
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa47240000000000bfc892",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1772767012,
      "updated": 1772767013
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa47250000000000bfc894",
      "text": "\t[~ 「人には価値がない」と言いつつ「『人には価値がない』ことへの『価値』」を見出しているのはお前なんじゃない？]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1772767013,
      "updated": 1772785472
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa475c0000000000bfc895",
      "text": "\t\tちょっと[ちくちく言葉]すぎるか",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1772767068,
      "updated": 1772767081
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa9ee000000000001c9ee6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772789473,
      "updated": 1772789473
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa9ee000000000001c9ee7",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772789473,
      "updated": 1772789478
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa9ee600000000001c9ee8",
      "text": " 差別語と、性あるいは生命自身に関わる搾取の言葉",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772789478,
      "updated": 1772789593
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa9eee00000000001c9ee9",
      "text": " \tつまり、両者を掛け合わせた「性的/生命への搾取を思わせる差別語」",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772789486,
      "updated": 1772803657
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa9f0400000000001c9eea",
      "text": " [hoagecko.icon]としては性産業への偏見に根ざした、いのちに関わる現場への差別語が特に心に来る",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772789508,
      "updated": 1772803690
    },
    {
      "id": "69aad66a0000000000b30179",
      "text": " \t[~ からゆきさん]など",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772803691,
      "updated": 1772803706
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa47250000000000bfc893",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1772767013,
      "updated": 1772767013
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa4eba000000000046666f",
      "text": " 何をもって強いと表現してるんだろうか[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772768954,
      "updated": 1772768971
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa6ddf0000000000154de2",
      "text": " 想定していたのは、各人の思う「[強い言葉]」ですね。厳格な定義はない[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772776927,
      "updated": 1772777088
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa97d000000000006f530",
      "text": " なるほど[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772792189,
      "updated": 1772792192
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa4ebc0000000000466670",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772768956,
      "updated": 1772768956
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa49500000000005fc15c",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772790935,
      "updated": 1772790935
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa49700000000005fc15e",
      "text": "\tこのページで本気でぶっ刺さるような言葉なんてかけるはずもなかろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772790935,
      "updated": 1772790962
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa4b500000000005fc15f",
      "text": " \t強い言葉のつもりで吐く言葉は[自分が一番傷つく言葉]なんだから",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772790965,
      "updated": 1772792153
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa49500000000005fc15d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772790935,
      "updated": 1772790935
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac2f70000000000a15850",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772798711,
      "updated": 1772798715
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac2f70000000000a15851",
      "text": "　いまさらだけど、[パワーワード]とは違う意味だよね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772798711,
      "updated": 1772798779
    },
    {
      "id": "69aac2f70000000000a15852",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772798711,
      "updated": 1772798711
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa9a2000000000006f531",
      "text": " [ワタシハリナックスチョットデキル][ワタシハリナックスチョットデキル.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772792226,
      "updated": 1772792261
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaa91000000000006f533",
      "text": " [なんとかなれーッ]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772792466,
      "updated": 1772792474
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaa9a5000000000006f532",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772792229,
      "updated": 1772792229
    },
    {
      "id": "69aad8a800000000007ee719",
      "text": "アイコン後置式に直したほうがいいだろうか[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772804265,
      "updated": 1772804293
    },
    {
      "id": "69aad8a200000000007ee718",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772804259,
      "updated": 1772804259
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa66630000000000decdf2",
      "text": "対となるページ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772775012,
      "updated": 1772775023
    },
    {
      "id": "69aa66550000000000decdf0",
      "text": "　[弱い言葉を書いてけ]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772774997,
      "updated": 1772775015
    }
  ]
}